                                    ضمانت برگشت کالا
                                </p>
                            </div>


                        </div>


                        <div class="col-6 col-lg-3 align-items-center d-flex">


                            <div class="slogan__item mx-auto text-center py-3">
                                <img src="images/icons/support1.svg" alt="">
